        depending on the kindOfVisibility this method calls the correspondent method and give it the correct input
        Parameters:
        visibility - visibility of the effect
        player - owner of the weapon
        movesAway - how many moves targets have to be away from the shooter
        exactly - if they have to be away EXACTLY moves away
        moves - how many moves the player can move during the effect
        Returns:
        list of reachable cells
